(Mabe 6.a3 is more circumspect.)} 6... c5 7. dxc5 dxc5 8. b3 g5 {#(A typical
Basman move, fights for e5, clears the h-file and gets the Bishop to g7, here
with tempi on Ktc3.)} 9. fxg5 Bg7 10. Bb2 hxg5 11. Nxg5 Nd7 12. Qf3 Bf6 $5 {
(To forestall 0-0-0 and tell Ktg5 not to be too optimistic about f7.)} 13. Nd5
