and there is no answer to Qh2+ and Qh1 mate.}) 36... Rh1+ 37. Ke2 Bxf3+ $1 38.
gxf3 ({if} 38. Rxf3 Qe1#) 38... Qg1 {With mate to follow White Resigns.} 0-1

