15. Nf4 $6 {My own opinion, not theory's!} 15... b5 $1 16. Nxe6 fxe6 17. Qa3
Bxd4 18. Bxd4 Qxd4+ 19. Kh1 Nc6 {
With a slight advantage to Black, as in Ji Y vs Deng k, China 1989.} 20. Rad1
